# Somnio gameplay-transport pinned trust roots.
#
# Let's Encrypt issues the production wss:// certificate (Traefik + ACME via
# Cloudflare DNS-01). Pinning the long-lived ISRG roots — not the 90-day leaf —
# means certificate renewals never break the shipped player. Both roots are
# included so a future RSA->ECDSA key-type switch (X1->X2) needs no client update.
#
# Scripts/inject-release-transport.sh embeds these into gameplayProductionTrustRootPEM
# in GameplayServerPin.swift at player-release packaging time.
#
# ISRG Root X1 (RSA)   SHA-256 96:BC:EC:06:26:49:76:F3:74:60:77:9A:CF:28:C5:A7:CF:E8:A3:C0:AA:E1:1A:8F:FC:EE:05:C0:BD:DF:08:C6
